p.k: Rachel Starr plots to set up her cheating husband, Xander Corvus, with hired escort Azul Hermosa so she can catch them in the act and cash in on a big divorce settlement. There's just one hitch though: Azul ends up seducing Rachel instead! Xander walks in on the two scissoring on the couch and pulls out his phone... and his dick, leading to a surprise threesome that Rachel passes off as an anniversary gift to avoid revealing her secret plan!
